!theme plain
left to right direction
title Interview â€” System Context\nFOMC Agent Lab

actor "Analyst / Reviewer" as User #E8F0FE
cloud "BLS LABSTAT\n(download.bls.gov)" as BLS #F5F5F5
cloud "DataUSA API\n(honolulu-api.datausa.io)" as DataUSA #F5F5F5

rectangle "FOMC Agent Pipeline" as System #E3F2FD {
  rectangle "Ingestion\n(raw landing)" as Ingest #E8F5E9
  rectangle "Parse/Update\n(processed)" as Parse #E8F5E9
  rectangle "Enrich\n(curated)" as Enrich #E8F5E9
  rectangle "CDC / Triggers\n(SQS + retries)" as CDC #FFF3E0
}

database "Object Storage\n(S3 raw/processed/curated)" as S3 #E8F5E9
queue "Queue\n(SQS)" as SQS #FFF3E0
rectangle "Static Site\n(Dashboard + Charts)" as Site #F3E5F5
rectangle "Observability\n(Logs/Metrics)" as Obs #F5F5F5

BLS --> Ingest : source data
DataUSA --> Ingest : source data
Ingest --> S3 : land raw bytes
Parse --> S3 : write tables
Enrich --> S3 : write derived datasets
CDC --> SQS : publish work items
SQS --> Parse : trigger on changes
SQS --> Enrich : trigger on changes
Enrich --> Site : publish JSON artifacts
System --> Obs : logs + metrics

User --> Site : view dashboard
User --> Obs : inspect failures\n(DLQ, logs)

@enduml
